title: Husky Liners “On the Hunt” - Mud Guards Product Video (:30)
description: Meet Austin Hanlon. He is a son that likes to go hunting with his father, and get dirty in the process. Husky Liners® form fit Mud Guards are made from durable, impact resistant all-weather thermoplastic that’s as tough as nails (or rocks for that matter). They’re easy to install, conform perfectly to your fenders, and protect your ride and those around you from the rage of the road.
tags: Husky Liners, Mud Guards, Mud Flaps, Husky
